Symbol.Script_3D:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, openingArchHeight = openingArchHeight, gs_lowerArchHeight = gs_lowerArchHeight, nArchResolution = gs_res, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! =============================================================================
shadow on pen WALL_VIEW_PEN resol gs_res
LowArcoffsx = A/2 - (RadArch - sqr(RadArch ^2 - gs_lowerArchHeight ^2))
if abs(WIDO_ORIG_DIST)<EPS then
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then mulz -1
addz -WIDO_SILL + WALL_THICKNESS/2
! --- Hotspot Editing in 3D --- unID=1
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, gs_shoulder_height, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, -1, 0, unID, gs_shoulder_height, 3 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, gs_shoulder_height, 0, unID, gs_shoulder_height, 2 : unID = unID + 1
hotspot 0, gs_shoulder_height, 0, unID, gs_lowerArchHeight, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, gs_lowerArchHeight, 3 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, gs_shoulder_height + gs_lowerArchHeight, 0, unID, gs_lowerArchHeight, 2 : unID = unID + 1
del 1
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then del 1 endif
! ============================================================================= ! Preview in Door Settings Dialog and in Listing ! =============================================================================
if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE # 0 | GLOB_FEEDBACK_MODE then if not(WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE) then addz -WIDO_SILL else addz WIDO_SILL - WALL_THICKNESS + WIDO_FRAME_THICKNESS endif
if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 1 | GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 3 then put A/2 + 0.2, -0.2, 8, A/2 + 0.2, B + 0.2, 8, -A/2 - 0.2, B + 0.2, 8, -A/2 - 0.2, -0.2, 8, A/2 + 0.2, -0.2, -1 endif
if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 2 then isPrism = 0 isExtrude = 1 gosub "putparameters"
extrude NSP/3, 0, 0, WALL_THICKNESS, 16+32, get(NSP) else isPrism = 1 isExtrude = 0 gosub "putparameters"
cprism_ WALL_MAT_A, WALL_MAT_B, WALL_MAT_EDGE, NSP/3, WALL_THICKNESS, get(NSP) endif del 1 if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE # 0 then end endif
! ============================================================================= ! Wallhole ! =============================================================================
offset = 0 if abs(WIDO_ORIG_DIST) > EPS then offset = WIDO_ORIG_DIST-(WIDO_ORIG_DIST^2-(A/2)^2)*0.5 endif
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! en ! ==============================================================================
"putparameters":
flag1 = 1+2+4+8+16 flag2 = 64+1+2+4+8+16 if isPrism then flag1 = 31 flag2 = 64+31 endif if isExtrude then flag1 = 0 flag2 = 1 endif
put A/2, 0, flag1, A/2, gs_shoulder_height, flag1, LowArcoffsx - EPS, gs_shoulder_height, flag1, LowArcoffsx, gs_shoulder_height, flag2, A/2 - RadArch, gs_shoulder_height + gs_lowerArchHeight, 900, 0, B, 3000 + flag1, -EPS, B, flag2, -A/2 + RadArch, gs_shoulder_height + gs_lowerArchHeight, 900, -LowArcoffsx, gs_shoulder_height, 3000 + flag2, -LowArcoffsx + EPS, gs_shoulder_height, flag1, -A/2, gs_shoulder_height, flag1, -A/2, 0, flag1, A/2, 0, -1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! =============================================================================
if not(gs_center_hpts_compatibility) then unID = 1 hotspot2 0,0, unID unID = unID + 1 endif
! ============================================================================= ! Arc in 2D - Straight Wall ! =============================================================================
if gs_arc_2D then line_type gs_brickw_lt toler 0.001
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then mul2 1, -1 endif add2 0, WIDO_SILL
mul2 1, -1 poly2_ 14,1, -A/2, 0, 1, -A*openingArchHeight*cos(4*U)+openingArchHeight*A-A/2, 0, 1, openingArchHeight*A-A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 900, 0, 4*U, 4001, -A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 1, openingArchHeight*A-A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 900, 0, 10*T, 4001, 0, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A-S, 1, -openingArchHeight*A+A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 900, 0, 10*T, 4001, A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 1, -openingArchHeight*A+A/2, -gs_lowerArchHeight*A, 900, 0, 4*U, 4001, A/2, 0, 0 del 1
del 1 + WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iTypeCurvedWallCut CUT_PARALLEL = 1 CUT_RADIAL = 2
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
if GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 7 | GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 8 then goto "MasterEnd" ! forward migration, backward migration
! ============================================================================= ! Main Definitions ! =============================================================================
EPS = 0.0001
iWindowShape = 16 ! SHAPE_HORSESHOE bParalellInCurvedWalls = (iTypeCurvedWallCut = CUT_PARALLEL)
curvedWall = abs(WIDO_ORIG_DIST) > EPS
RadArch = ((A/2) ^2 + (openingArchHeight - gs_lowerArchHeight) ^2) / A
"MasterEnd":
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
aaa = GLOB_ELEVATION ! #92488
! ============================================================================= ! GS Door Openeing Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Door Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! ============================================================================= ! Orientation ! =============================================================================
ac_OpeningSide = "" parameters ac_OpeningSide = ac_OpeningSide
! IFC Parameters -------------------------------------------------------------- call "IFC_optype_door" parameters all
if A < EPS then parameters A = 0.01
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "openingArchHeight" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then gs_shoulder_height = B - openingArchHeight parameters gs_shoulder_height = gs_shoulder_height endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_shoulder_height" then openingArchHeight = B - gs_shoulder_height parameters openingArchHeight = openingArchHeight endif
values "gs_shoulder_height" range [0, B - A/2] values "openingArchHeight" range [A/2, B] values "gs_lowerArchHeight" range [0, min(openingArchHeight - A/2, openingArchHeight / 2)] values "A" range [0, 2*B] values "B" range [A/2, )
values{2} "iTypeCurvedWallCut" CUT_PARALLEL, `Параллельно`, CUT_RADIAL, `Радиально` values "gs_res" range[3,) values "gs_frame_thk" range[0,]
parameters gs_fontsize = abs(gs_fontsize) values "gs_fontsize" range(0,]
! Wall Contour Left/Right --------------------------------------------------------------
gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour) parameters gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour)
gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour) parameters gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour)
!**************** Swedish list parameter control ********************** if gs_SWE_listParams_contr > 0 then call "SWE_ListParameters_control" parameters gs_SWE_listParams_contr = gs_SWE_listParams_contr, swe_list_d1 = swe_list_d1 endif
! ============================================================================= ! Zone Recognitions for Doors - Parapet wall Inset value calculation ! at Empty Openings: ! GLOB_ELEVATION - conditional - Zona`s flowing only at zero sill ! WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE - UNconditional - its always flipped inside WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE = 1 ! REVEAL (WIDO_SILL) - conditional - like its flipped outside (design) ! =============================================================================
ZONE_RECOGNITION_NONE = 0 ZONE_RECOGNITION_FULL = 1 ZONE_RECOGNITION_OUTSIDE = 2 ZONE_RECOGNITION_INSIDE = 3
if WIDO_REVEAL_SIDE then pwi = ZONE_RECOGNITION_INSIDE else pwi = ZONE_RECOGNITION_OUTSIDE endif
parameters pwi = pwi
